review:
This game is extremely fun. I have been enjoying it for a long while before deciding to finally give my impressions of it;

It is a great game, with a few limitations, that has incredible potential. The games you can make with it can feel extraordinarily fulfilling, and often do once you commit yourself to creating unique classes, monsters, and npcs, with the nifty model editor. The community behind the game is also impressively welcoming for something of its scale, and have all been more than happy to test out the newest preview build for the upcoming update for a while, which has been seeing consistent improvement and fixes from an active, albeit small, development team.

To say I recommend this game is an understatement. See what you can make in the game. The AI subscribers have some interesting tricks up their sleeves for what appeals to them and it's very intriguing to try and decipher what they really need to stay invested in your quaint little dream game.
